            "reviews": "“What a trip.”<br>5/5 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2017/jun/27/nex-machina-review-a-pure-brilliant-shoot-em-up\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >The Guardian</a><br><br>“Housemarque has just made the game of its career.”<br>Essential – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-06-20-nex-machina-review\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Eurogamer</a><br><br>“Nex Machina is a game that confidently meets expectations. It's difficult, intensely satisfying, and packed with enough secrets and lofty secondary objectives to keep you enraptured for hours.”<br>9/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/nex-machina-review/1900-6416704/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Gamespot</a><br>",
